        "subject": "LU-3538 cos: combo patch for DNE COS support",
        "message": "LU-3538 cos: combo patch for DNE COS support\n\nThis combo patch contains three COS patches, and used for\nperformance test, not intended to land.\n1. add COS for cross-MDT lock.\n2. add strict COS lock to elimite dependency between mkdir and\n   subseqent operations.\n3. enable COS on DNE by default.\n\nLustre-Change: http://review.whamcloud.com/12530\nLustre-Change: http://review.whamcloud.com/13139\nLustre-Change: http://review.whamcloud.com/15844\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <lai.siyao@intel.com>\nSigned-off-by: wang di <di.wang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I68ce97a9d7f84960348e4170b8141e35ad07db67\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
